00:23:13,018 --> 00:23:14,561
The Hong family's popularity

525
00:23:14,602 --> 00:23:15,979
and ability to capture
people's hearts,

526
00:23:16,021 --> 00:23:17,188
it's quite astonishing.

527
00:23:20,316 --> 00:23:21,776
- [Koyu Voiceover] Lord
Shoka has Lord Reishin and I

