00:23:21,818 --> 00:23:23,111
in his grasp.

529
00:23:23,153 --> 00:23:24,988
Shurei has the king
completely under her control

530
00:23:25,030 --> 00:23:26,614
and they have someone
as outstanding

531
00:23:26,656 --> 00:23:29,826
as Seiran working
for them. (chuckles)

532
00:23:31,327 --> 00:23:32,662
If those three put
their minds to it,

533
00:23:32,704 --> 00:23:33,872
they could probably take control

534
00:23:33,913 --> 00:23:35,749
of this entire country tomorrow.

