00:25:04,838 --> 00:25:06,006
Boy, it's been really busy.

539
00:25:06,047 --> 00:25:07,841
It feels like it's
taking its toll.

540
00:25:07,882 --> 00:25:09,300
No, pull yourself
together, Shurei.

